23 SECTION 3. AMENDMENT. Section 15.1-31-05 of the North Dakota Century Code is
24 amended and reenacted as follows:
25 15.1-31-05. Open enrollment - Transportation.
26 A school district of residence may provide transportation to a student participating in open
27 enrollment. If a district of residence does not provide transportation to a student participating in
28 open enrollment, transportation may be provided by the admitting district. A school district may
29 not receive transportation aid disbursements under subdivision a of subsection 1 of section
30 15.1-27-26.1 or subsection 3 of section 15.1-27-26.1 forinclude any factors associated with
31 transporting students who are participating in open enrollment, or who are enrolled pursuant to
